87b56509607f03526e","tid":521244,"uid":13468,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"2014年3、4月開始，田繼偉多次將地塞米松（Dexamethasone，類固醇的一種）注射液、慶大霉素（Gentamicin，抗生素）混合糖水倒入張飲水用的杯子和保溫瓶內。地塞米松沒有氣味，味道略苦。"},{"pid":"bf14bc4f9ae4890f8a7c89821d921af14ca2bd21","tid":521244,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac5ea7da299e61da13b3dc0f4fb79319331b866","tid":521244,"uid":85284,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"03ffc004cab3246391866e012fb76e1e56598965","tid":521244,"uid":1166,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"所以返工第一時間係要洗杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"無用架<br />\n強國有一個龐大組織<br />\n非常擅長同經驗豐富<br />\n點樣經飲食甚至經空氣媒介去落五花八門嘅藥去整／害人<br />\n尤其近呢十年<br />\n香港應該都有唔少受害者<br />\n不過可能佢哋連死嗰時都仲係懵然不知"},{"pid":"7805afd0f3a4de0b8194ee2273c4841a9389f03d","tid":521244,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"啲女人好撚古惑架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04e5120876c0c387c1c91c4a32c5f693fc68be8","tid":521244,"uid":88841,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"ef6bc1a56890d2e9fa9f7255b7bb321831861a1c","tid":521244,"uid":29270,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"quote":{"pid":"d25a1f44b0f220f78b299d1f7301bc0da79e09cb","tid":521244,"uid":53126,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"e3313892e2855a598e8b4c0faeee6c58226d2a99","tid":521244,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":29,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T03:12:48.000Z","msg":"老鼠藥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T03:20:15.000Z","msg":"閱讀理解拎F?<br />\n<br />\n其後警察將田繼偉拘捕。經法醫鑑定，張女士由於長期大量攝入<span style=\"color: red;\">激素類藥物</span>致兩側股骨頭缺血壞死，構成重傷二級；庫欣氏症候群，構成重傷二級；左眼白內障，構成輕傷二級；胸、腰椎體壓縮骨折，構成輕傷一級。"},"citedBy":